													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[SCENE] Gale startles awake and jumps to his feet, revealing a winged cat perched on an object (stump? chair? whatever will help Tara be at Gale's eye-level while he's standing. The idea is that their dialogue will be cheap from here on out, i.e. Gale won't have to talk and emote while sitting or laying down, but standing in normal position)."
